 285:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal.c **** /**
 286:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal.c ****   * @brief This function is called to increment a global variable "uwTick"
